description: Try our easy to follow Corn & Scrambled Egg Wrap recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Corn & Scrambled Egg Wrap Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Spread avocado down centre of mountain bread. Top with spinach leaves and tomato. Spoon over egg mixture and season with freshly ground black pepper. Fold sides over to enclose.
